My family and don't forget your family.

37:29.443 --> 37:34.249
Sometimes we go straight to like going out into the workplace and we stop being salt in our own families.

37:34.269 --> 37:36.372
Your family needs that too, your home who you live with.

37:36.753 --> 37:37.554
They need that too.

37:38.835 --> 37:39.797
But where has God sent you?

37:40.738 --> 37:42.300
He's not sent you there by accident.

37:42.941 --> 37:47.126
And do you think of yourself as being sent, whether it's in your home raising your children or into a workplace?

37:48.188 --> 37:49.810
Just as Jacob was sent

37:50.050 --> 37:51.992
to Israel, so God has actually sent you there.

37:52.052 --> 37:53.193
He has you there on purpose.

37:54.494 --> 37:55.115
Are you a blessing?

37:56.216 --> 37:58.298
Do you make the places that you are taste good?

37:59.979 --> 38:00.820
This is what we're called to be.

38:01.701 --> 38:02.402
And we can only do that.

38:02.422 --> 38:06.606
If we come in here, remember who we are to be sent out there.

38:08.107 --> 38:08.888
Maybe grow in this.

38:09.188 --> 38:18.257
Maybe grow in our ability to be strong as we are sent that we can live in this world, but not of this world, spreading the salt of God's kingdom wherever we find ourselves.

38:19.018 --> 38:19.538
Pray with me.

38:20.866 --> 38:27.133
Merciful God and heaven, we give you thanks for your goodness.

38:29.977 --> 38:35.043
We give you thanks that you've called us out of the kingdom of darkness and placed us in the kingdom of light.

38:35.063 --> 38:48.178
I pray that you would strengthen us in your kingdom, that you would strengthen our witness, that you strengthen our love, that you strengthen our convictions, that you would make us a blessing people in this city.

38:50.658 --> 38:54.906
We pray that you continue to grow this in us by faith and you and you alone.

38:56.416 --> 38:56.818
Amen.

